{"synckey":1638701011,"updated":[{"bookId":"807498","bookmarkId":"807498_10_2386-2530","chapterUid":10,"markText":"爱情包含以下部分：第一是尊重，爱一个人就要先尊重对方，包括尊重他的选择、他的喜好等等；第二是理解，能够设身处地站在对方的立场上去考虑问题，能够洞察他的内心世界和所思所想；第三是真正的关心，在生活方面、情感方面，处处替他着想；第四是责任感，一旦爱上一个人，就应当为他负责，承担一些社会责任。","range":"2386-2530","createTime":1638701011,"type":1},{"bookId":"807498","bookmarkId":"807498_10_2322-2346","chapterUid":10,"markText":"理解与尊重，积极为对方着想是爱情非常重要的内涵。","range":"2322-2346","createTime":1638701000,"type":1},{"bookId":"807498","bookmarkId":"807498_10_507-541","chapterUid":10,"markText":"真正的爱是理解、尊重、体谅与责任，更是一种由衷的欣赏和一颗宽容的心。","range":"507-541","createTime":1638700936,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"04 什么是“爱”？","chapterUid":10,"chapterIdx":10}],"book":{"bookId":"807498","version":1410253527,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/72/YueWen_807498/s_YueWen_807498.jpg","title":"学习爱：青音和心理专家贾晓明关于恋爱心理的对话","author":"中央人民广播电台","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KUOw5hogVr_QaexvG@oLWU","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#320f26"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#39062a"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#40002e"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#492536"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#521e39"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#5b123c"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#653b4a"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#70334c"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#7b294e"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#8f0052"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8a4d62"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a03c64"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#7d5461"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#bc587b"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#966f79"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b1607a"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b08993"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#bf8293"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#cb7c93"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#e36c94"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#e796ac"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#f48fac"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff85ad"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#e4bec6"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#f5b7c6"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ff9dc6"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#eedfe2"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffb6e0"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#cb7c93"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#e796ac"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3E5E8"},{"key